{
  "stem": "21349.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lawrence River in Canada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, when we came to Quebec, we made a little stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a man came to our boat from the Jewish immigrant Aid Society.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said to us, I'm supposed to talk to all the refugees-- refugees.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were refugees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I have to tell them that the Canadian government told us to bring you as quickly as possible to your destination, which is Yorkton, Saskatchewan.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So when you come to Montreal, I'll be there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I will arrange it for you so that you leave tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, we arrived in Montreal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a very nice trip, very beautiful trip on the St.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Lawrence River from Quebec to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We came to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's a big city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we came there after 9 o'clock in the evening, Thursday evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, the boat company has a-- has a regulation that if people come there after 9 o'clock in the evening, they can either go out or they can stay on the boat 'til next morning.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we had no one to await us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The other refugees on the boat had family waiting for them and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had no one there, so we stayed-- we stayed 'til the next morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We stayed 'til the next morning and then we went out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then the man came and he took us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He said, I bring you to a little restaurant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I bring you to the train station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And from there, the train will leave at 12 o'clock to Saskatchewan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's a five-day trip, because the Canadian railroad at that time, you see, had mainly freight trains, and they stop at every little village.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't want to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
